events.text: one important distinction must be drawn between the words dissection and vivisection
a distinction that would appear to be lost on you.
the hallways and corridors of the house are its veins, providing circulation coursing throughout its brain.
a staircase bears more than a passing resemblance, both physically and symbolically, to a spine.
have you not been paying attention?
did it not occur to you that as an organism existing within a greater organism, your intrusion would be felt?
